Package com.saicone.settings.type

Class Types

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saicone.settings.type.Types
  • public class Types
extends Object
    Utility class to collect common and registrable type parsers.

      • parse

        @Nullable
public static <T> T parse​(@NotNull
                          @NotNull Class<T> type,
                          @Nullable
                          @Nullable Object object)
        Parse any object by providing a type class to find previously registered type parser.
        This method can also parse into primitive class objects and instead of null the failed value to return will be MIN value for number types, FALSE for boolean and empty for char.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type result.
        Parameters:
        type - the class type.
        object - the object to parse.
        Returns:
        a converted value type, null otherwise.

      • parse

public static <T> T parse​(@NotNull
                          @NotNull Class<T> type,
                          @Nullable
                          @Nullable Object object,
                          @Nullable
                          T def)
        Parse any object by providing a type class to find previously registered type parser.
        This method can also parse into primitive class objects and instead of default object the failed value to return will be MIN value for number types, FALSE for boolean and empty for char.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type result.
        Parameters:
        type - the class type.
        object - the object to parse.
        def - the type object to return if parser fails or doesn't exist.
        Returns:
        a converted value type, default object otherwise.
